"With Facebook it all falls away - you go directly to them."
Others say that the site offers an opportunity to identify and solve social health problems.
A recent study by Dr. Megan Moreno from the University of Wisconsin, Madison, and her colleagues found that students who discussed their full noise on Facebook are significantly more inclined to drink problems than students who are silent on this topic.
